        .question__plus
          span
          span
        .question-item_content(data-id="2") No, matching supports any amount of trading pairs. 

      .question-item.faq_btn_js(data-id="3")
        span What is the capacity of Matching Engine?
        .question__plus
          span
          span
        .question-item_content(data-id="3") B2Trader Matching engine can fulfill up to 10,000 requests per second.
      
      .question-item.faq_btn_js(data-id="8")
        span Can I host the matching engine on my servers?
        .question__plus
          span
          span
        .question-item_content(data-id="8") No, you can choose only hosting location. We use AWS solution and provide full support and maintenance of the servers.
      
      .question-item.faq_btn_js(data-id="9")
