        .question__plus
          span
          span
        .question-item_content(data-id="9") B2Trader allows to execute Limit orders, Fill-or-Kill & Immediate-or-Cancel Market orders and Stop orders as well.
      
      .question-item.faq_btn_js(data-id="10")
