        span Is B2Trader suitable only for cryptocurrencies? 
        .question__plus
          span
          span
        .question-item_content(data-id="4") No, it's suitable as well for MTF Brokers, Security Exchanges,  Market Makers, Spot FX Brokers and EMIs.

